N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 30.2 - Eligibility

State Regulations

Any registrant of a fleet who desires to participate in the
fleet registration program shall make application on or before June 1st of any
year to have its registrations converted to an October 31st permanent fleet
date. Notes
